<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Applewood Park</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Applewood Park was established in 1982 and has been designed according to a well-structured master plan for its landscape.</p>

            <p class="par-xl">Home to more than 6,400 residents, the community in Applewood Park is ideal for young couples, growing families, as well as retirees. </p>

            <p class="par-lg">Applewood Park Real estate offers a variety of housing options ranging from starter homes, to bungalows and even apartment condos that are typically listed at an average sale price of $370,000. </p>

